# Implementation Plan: ATS v3.0 Phase 1 (The Intelligent Foundation)

This phase focuses on establishing the **Intelligent Department** as a decoupled entity from the **ATS Executor**. We will implement the data recording infrastructure (Pool Memory), the Intelligent Gate (Rule-Based Filtering), and real-time Smart Money tracking via Bullpen.fi.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Daily Retrain Cycle:** We have switched from Weekly to **Daily Retrain** (every 288 windows) to ensure the model stays fresh with the latest Polymarket dynamics.
> **Bullpen CLI:** Integration requires the `bullpen` CLI to be installed on the machine.

> [!NOTE]
> **Telegram Verbosity:** Telegram notifications will now include Window Snapshots, Outcomes (WIN/LOSS), and Retrain stats. Ensure the bot is not in a shared channel if you prefer privacy for this volume of data.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. [NEW] Intelligent Department (`Intelligent/`)

#### [NEW] [memory.py](file:///c:/Users/Razer/OneDrive/Desktop/hedge/Intelligent/memory.py)
*   Implements `PoolMemory` class using SQLite.
*   Schema: `window_id`, `confidence`, `convergence_score`, `news_impact`, `bullpen_signal`, `features_snapshot` (JSON), `ats_status`, `pnl`, `outcome`.
*   **Telegram Logic:** Sends a snapshot notification when a new record is created.

#### [NEW] [bullpen_connector.py](file:///c:/Users/Razer/OneDrive/Desktop/hedge/Intelligent/bullpen_connector.py)
*   Interface for **Bullpen CLI**.
*   Runs `bullpen polymarket data smart-money --output json`.
*   Parses top trader signals to calculate a `bullpen_sentiment_score` (-1 to 1).

#### [NEW] [openrouter_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/Razer/OneDrive/Desktop/hedge/Intelligent/openrouter_agent.py)
*   Interface untuk **OpenRouter API**.
*   Mengirimkan context (News + Bullpen Data + Binance Metrics) ke LLM (e.g., DeepSeek) untuk mendapatkan *Reasoning* dan *Confidence Score*.
*   Bertindak sebagai "Final Judge" sebelum `gate_decision` dikeluarkan.

#### [NEW] [feature_builder.py](file:///c:/Users/Razer/OneDrive/Desktop/hedge/Intelligent/feature_builder.py)
*   Connects to Binance WebSocket (aggTrade, Depth).
*   Calculates CVD (Cumulative Volume Delta) and Order Book Imbalance.
*   Stores snapshots in memory for the Gate to consume at T-25.

#### [NEW] [gate.py](file:///c:/Users/Razer/OneDrive/Desktop/hedge/Intelligent/gate.py)
*   **Ensemble Engine:** Combines Binance features + CryptoPanic News + Bullpen Smart Money.
*   **Daily Retrain Loop:** Triggers after every 288 records using `PoolMemory`.
*   **Telegram Logic:** Sends a summary of the new model accuracy/loss after each retrain.

